RubbishRouter Light
Scalable Community-Powered Waste Tracking

RubbishRouter Light is a "Waze-style" crowdsourcing platform for municipal waste management. It allows residents to track the progress of waste collection vehicles without the need for municipal GPS hardware.

✨ Key Features
Multi-Muni Identity: Scoped data for any municipality via URL parameters (?muni=Name).

Crowdsourced Breadcrumbs: Live map updates when neighbors report their bins are emptied.

Gamified Rewards: Monthly Star Ranking (Silver to Gold) for active contributors.

Business Ready: Integrated R70/week advertising slots and R15/month resident subscriptions.

🚀 Commercial Model
This app is designed for private operation. Income from subscriptions and advertising is managed directly through the integrated PayFast portal.
